\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gamechanger\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would not want it to happen to anyone else.\\\"\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Happily, that silver medal still felt like a win.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"silver medal\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"a win\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How could it not when in the moment of claiming it she turned unexpectedly to see her son in the arms of husband James, who had driven down to Ch\\u00e2teauroux the day before to surprise her?\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2236, \"end\": 2241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.937653432925824, \"rank\": 0.06649165328565299, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}, {\"begin\": 2266, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LB_Ch\\u00e2teauroux\", \"score\": 0.5620079632512844, \"rank\": 0.7757073491969764, \"text\": \"Ch\\u00e2teauroux\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LB_Ch\\u00e2teauroux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LB_Ch\\u00e2teauroux\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"her son\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"the arms\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For a woman who had struggled through the disappointment ofTokyo, where a positive Covid test the day before her departure erased a whole Olympic cycle and left 