ions are real, and they are entitled to them.\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 3896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3810, \"to\": 3816}, {\"ngram\": \"a situation\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 3839}, {\"ngram\": \"their emotions\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I am honest I do not think Tokyo is something I will ever fully get over.\", \"from\": 3898, \"to\": 3975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3929, \"end\": 3934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7444215287108498, \"rank\": 0.34332490068358745, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 3947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the worst point of my life.\", \"from\": 3976, \"to\": 4010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the worst point\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 3998}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 4002, \"to\": 4009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Never experienced pain and upset like it.\", \"from\": 4011, \"to\": 4052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4033}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Straight afterwards I felt like I was dealing with it, but once the whole thing died down and you go into the winter months.\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the whole thing\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4132}, {\"ngram\": \"the winter months\", \"from\": 4159, \"to\": 4176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's something called the Olympic blues.\", \"from\": 4179, \"to\": 4220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4185, \"to\": 4194}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic blues\", \"from\": 4202, \"to\": 4219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have all this build-up to the games and then everyone forgets about it.\", \"from\": 4221, \"to\": 4296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all this build-up\", \"from\": 4230, \"to\": 4247}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 4251, \"to\": 4260}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 4270, \"to\": 4278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was the point I really struggled.\", \"from\": 4297, \"to\": 4335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I put myself in such a bad place.\", \"from\": 4336, \"to\": 4369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a bad place\", \"from\": 4352, \"to\": 4368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not want to do my sport anymore.\", \"from\": 4370, \"to\": 4408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my sport\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just wanted to be an average person working nine to five.\\\"\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4469, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an average person\", \"from\": 4429, \"to\": 4446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seeking the necessary help was key.\", \"from\": 4471, \"to\": 4506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the necessary help\", \"from\": 4479, \"to\": 4497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went to counselling.\", \"from\": 4507, \"to\": 4530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"counselling\", \"from\": 4518, \"to\": 4529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not ashamed to talk about it.\", \"from\": 4531, \"to\": 4565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not like to label it as depression or anxiety.\", \"from\": 4566, \"to\": 4617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"depression\", \"from\": 4595, \"to\": 4605}, {\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 4609, \"to\": 4616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am generally a very happy person, and look at the positives, but I think we go through times where we struggle, when there are certain situations or relationship problems or whatever it may be.\", \"from\": 4618, \"to\": 4813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very happy person\", \"from\": 4633, \"to\": 4652}, {\"ngram\": \"the positives\", \"from\": 4666, \"to\": 4679}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 4707, \"to\": 4712}, {\"ngram\": \"certain situations\", \"from\": 4747, \"to\": 4765}, {\"ngram\": \"relationship problems\", \"from\": 4769, \"to\": 4790}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 4802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I have never experienced anything like I went through with Tokyo.\", \"from\": 4814, \"to\": 4883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4877, \"end\": 4882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7444215287108498, \"rank\": 0.34332490068358745, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really sad most days and lost with what direction I wanted to take in my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 4884, \"to\": 4969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what direction\", \"from\": 4925, \"to\": 4939}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 4960, \"to\": 4967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shooting is not football or tennis.\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 5006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shooting\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4979}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 4987, \"to\": 4995}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 4999, \"to\": 5005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not have the luxury of quitting.\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the luxury\", \"from\": 5024, \"to\": 5034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The only reason I continued was for money, to keep a roof over my head and pay my mortgage.\", \"from\": 5048, \"to\": 5140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only reason\", \"from\": 5049, \"to\": 5064}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 5085, \"to\": 5090}, {\"ngram\": \"a roof\", \"from\": 5100, \"to\": 5106}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 5112, \"to\": 5119}, {\"ngram\": \"my mortgage\", \"from\": 5128, \"to\": 5139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It took me a good one to two years to accept what had happened and learn to look to the future instead of living in the past.\", \"from\": 5141, \"to\": 5266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 5166, \"to\": 5175}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 5225, \"to\": 5235}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 5257, \"to\": 5265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had a responsibility to my sponsors and lottery funding.\", \"from\": 5267, \"to\": 5325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a responsibility\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5289}, {\"ngram\": \"my sponsors\", \"from\": 5293, \"to\": 5304}, {\"ngram\": \"lottery funding\", \"from\": 5309, \"to\": 5324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was lucky and grateful to have that, and it helped get me get through.\", \"from\": 5326, \"to\": 5398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know it sounds cheesy and we thank our sponsors a lot, but I would not be shooting without them.\", \"from\": 5400, \"to\": 5499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our sponsors\", \"from\": 5438, \"to\": 5450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the reality for us.\", \"from\": 5500, \"to\": 5526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reality\", \"from\": 5507, \"to\": 5518}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5523, \"to\": 5525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are definitely looked after.\", \"from\": 5527, \"to\": 5558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have some great sponsors like Clays, Beretta and Eley Hawk.\", \"from\": 5559, \"to\": 5620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some great sponsors\", \"from\": 5566, \"to\": 5585}, {\"ngram\": \"Clays\", \"from\": 5591, \"to\": 5596}, {\"ngram\": \"Beretta\", \"from\": 5598, \"to\": 5605}, {\"ngram\": \"Eley Hawk\", \"from\": 5610, \"to\": 5619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without them I could not continue in the sport.\", \"from\": 5621, \"to\": 5668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 5658, \"to\": 5667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not like the big sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 5669, \"to\": 5701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the big sports\", \"from\": 5685, \"to\": 5699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not yet.\", \"from\": 5703, \"to\": 5711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rutter hopes her story, the rise from the trauma of Tokyo, the controversy in Paris, will bring new eyes to shooting.\", \"from\": 5712, \"to\": 5829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5764, \"end\": 5769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7444215287108498, \"rank\": 0.34332490068358745, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 5790, \"end\": 5795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.977749661914943e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her story\", \"from\": 5725, \"to\": 5734}, {\"ngram\": \"the rise\", \"from\": 5736, \"to\": 5744}, {\"ngram\": \"the trauma\", \"from\": 5750, \"to\": 5760}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 5771, \"to\": 5786}, {\"ngram\": \"new eyes\", \"from\": 5808, \"to\": 5816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And she has a new clothing line to spice up her life, and maybe yours.\", \"from\": 5830, \"to\": 5900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new clothing line\", \"from\": 5842, \"to\": 5861}, {\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 5874, \"to\": 5882}, {\"ngram\": \"maybe yours\", \"from\": 5888, \"to\": 5899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's called Ukiyo.\", \"from\": 5901, \"to\": 5920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5914, \"end\": 5919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukiyo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ukiyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukiyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukiyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was looking for something that represented my journey, from the struggles of Tokyo to this next chapter in my life.\", \"from\": 5921, \"to\": 6038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6000, \"end\": 6005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.7444215287108498, \"rank\": 0.34332490068358745, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5939, \"to\": 5948}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 5966, \"to\": 5976}, {\"ngram\": \"the struggles\", \"from\": 5983, \"to\": 5996}, {\"ngram\": \"this next chapter\", \"from\": 6009, \"to\": 6026}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 6030, \"to\": 6037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's Japanese for living in the moment, detaching from life's problems.\", \"from\": 6039, \"to\": 6110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 6067, \"to\": 6077}, {\"ngram\": \"life's problems\", \"from\": 6094, \"to\": 6109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I instantly knew it was the right name.\", \"from\": 6111, \"to\": 6150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right name\", \"from\": 6135, \"to\": 6149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have designed a range - shooting vests, waterproofs, leggings etc.\", \"from\": 6152, \"to\": 6221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a range - shooting vests\", \"from\": 6169, \"to\": 6193}, {\"ngram\": \"waterproofs\", \"from\": 6195, \"to\": 6206}, {\"ngram\": \"leggings\", \"from\": 6208, \"to\": 6216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea is to change the stereotypes around our sport, all the tweed, the male farmer.\", \"from\": 6222, \"to\": 6309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 6222, \"to\": 6230}, {\"ngram\": \"the stereotypes\", \"from\": 6244, \"to\": 6259}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 6267, \"to\": 6276}, {\"ngram\": \"the male farmer\", \"from\": 6293, \"to\": 6308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to encourage young people to get into this sport.\", \"from\": 6310, \"to\": 6366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 6330, \"to\": 6342}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 6355, \"to\": 6365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not have to wear tweed and wellies to shoot.\", \"from\": 6367, \"to\": 6418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tweed\", \"from\": 6391, \"to\": 6396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Personally I do not like tweed, I do not like green, I do not like wellies.\", \"from\": 6420, \"to\": 6496, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tweed\", \"from\": 6446, \"to\": 6451}, {\"ngram\": \"wellies\", \"from\": 6488, \"to\": 6495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I like my trainers and active wear.\", \"from\": 6497, \"to\": 6532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my trainers\", \"from\": 6504, \"to\": 6515}, {\"ngram\": \"active wear\", \"from\": 6520, \"to\": 6531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I put on my shooting jacket I want to feel positive.\", \"from\": 6533, \"to\": 6590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my shooting jacket\", \"from\": 6547, \"to\": 6565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you look good and feel good it gives you the confidence to go out and perform.\\\"\", \"from\": 6591, \"to\": 6673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the confidence\", \"from\": 6635, \"to\": 6649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amber Rutter is a brand ambassador for Clays, London's most advanced virtual shooting experience.\", \"from\": 6675, \"to\": 6772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6721, \"end\": 6727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999998132170905, \"rank\": 1.8677819862439906e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amber Rutter\", \"from\": 6675, \"to\": 6687}, {\"ngram\": \"a brand ambassador\", \"from\": 6691, \"to\": 6709}, {\"ngram\": \"Clays\", \"from\": 6714, \"to\": 6719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Impartial news + intelligent debate All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 6774, \"to\": 6831, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Impartial news + intelligent debate\", \"from\": 6774, \"to\": 6809}, {\"ngram\": \"All rights\", \"from\": 6810, \"to\": 6820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2026 Associated Newspapers Limited.\", \"from\": 6832, \"to\": 6869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a9\", \"from\": 6832, \"to\": 6833}]}]}"